videos.description: Tre Harbison's 1-yard touchdown run ties the game at 7-7 late in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Northern Illinois ties it up

videos.description: Marcus Childers runs for 22 yards to flip the field for Northern Illinois
videos.headline: Childers breaks free for big run

videos.description: Logan Woodside connects with Diontae Johnson for an 89 yards to set up first-and-goal for Toledo.
videos.headline: Woodside to Johnson for big air and big gain

videos.description: Logan Woodside fumbles at the goal line and Jawuan Johnson recovers for Northern Illinois.
videos.headline: Woodside's fumble costly for Toledo

videos.description: Trevon Mathis' interception off the deflection stops a Northern Illinois drive for Toledo.
videos.headline: Big stop for the Toledo defense

videos.description: Terry Swanson's 4-yard touchdown run gives Toledo its first lead of the game.
videos.headline: Swanson stretches for Toledo TD

videos.description: Marcus Jones runs for 29 yards to set up Northern Illinois deep in Toledo territory.
videos.headline: Northern Illinois in scoring position thanks to a big run

videos.description: Marcus Childers' 1-yard touchdown run reclaims the lead for the Huskies.
videos.headline: Northern Illinois reclaims the lead

videos.description: Logan Woodside hits Darryl Richards for a 31-yard pass play deep in Northern Illinois territory.
videos.headline: Woodside to Richards put Toledo on the move

videos.description: Terry Swanson's 1-yard touchdown run pushes the lead to 24-14 late in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Swanson's third TD extends the lead for Toledo

videos.description: Jackson Abresch's block punt leads to a Huskies field goal to cut the deficit to 24-17 in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Special Teams for Northern Illinois comes up big

videos.description: Trevon Mathis' second interception of the game stops Northern Illinois' drive in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Mathis comes up big again for Toledo
